## Description {#details}

This class holds an abstract representation of an Accelerator Table, consisting of a sequence of buckets, each bucket containint a sequence of <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/acceltablebase/hashdata">HashData</a> entries.

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/user">User</a> of DwarfEmitterImpl should call initialization code for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/asmprinter">AsmPrinter</a>:

The class is parameterized by the type of entries it holds. The type template parameter also defines the hash function to use for hashing names.

<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a2c23d23778140065e285b5263d7d905a">InitializeAllTargetInfos()</a>; <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a162474ccafa6e8ccf58b2b60e7c63845">InitializeAllTargetMCs()</a>; <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ad27eabc8391834dce3a68261f8a334db">InitializeAllTargets()</a>; <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#af12a586afbaec83aa9cd8b7e9ab0c116">InitializeAllAsmPrinters()</a>;
